pageContext.claim: “The country has had tremendous support from Meadows and Jordan and Devin Nunes and so many of the names that you saw yesterday, performed so well. I mean, they performed so well, and they worked so hard because they saw this was a scam. This was an illegal takeover, as you would say in the business world. I mean, this was -- this was a coup attempt, in my opinion. And this is the United States.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump falsely says the investigation by the Special Counsel -- appointed by his Justice Department -- amounted to an attempted coup.
